place.name: CHAPEL OF GARIOCH
place.gazetteerText: Chapel of Garioch, par. (containing Pitcaple ry. sta.) and vil., in co. and 21 m. NW. of Aberdeen, 13,059 ac., pop. 1923; in the par. is the battlefield of Harlaw (1411). (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
